{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01DaXg6soY1vwmK6tLJ97jit","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Quarkus 3.30.5 -> Spring Boot 3.4.3\n**Overall outcome:** Success - all 137 smoke tests passing\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus BOM/dependencies with Spring Boot starter-parent and starters\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Migrated from Quarkus to Spring Boot property format\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/request/RequestBean.java: Refactored from JAX-RS to Spring MVC (@RestController, @GetMapping, etc.)\n- Dockerfile: Changed CMD from \"mvn quarkus:run\" to \"java -jar\" with Spring Boot fat JAR\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/RosterApplication.java: Spring Boot application entry point\n- smoke.py: Comprehensive smoke test suite (137 assertions)\n- CHANGELOG.md: Complete migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/client/RosterClient.java: JAX-RS client (incompatible without JAX-RS client dependency)\n- src/main/docker/Dockerfile.jvm: Quarkus-specific Dockerfile\n- src/main/docker/Dockerfile.legacy-jar: Quarkus-specific Dockerfile\n- src/main/docker/Dockerfile.native: Quarkus-specific Dockerfile\n- src/main/docker/Dockerfile.native-micro: Quarkus-specific Dockerfile\n\nUnchanged (compatible with both frameworks):\n- All entity classes (Player, Team, League, SummerLeague, WinterLeague) - standard Jakarta Persistence\n- All DTO classes (PlayerDetails, TeamDetails, LeagueDetails)\n- IncorrectSportException\n- Request interface\n```\n\n### Key Migration Decisions\n\n1. **JAX-RS -> Spring MVC**: Replaced all JAX-RS annotations (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`, `@DELETE`, `@PathParam`, `@QueryParam`, `@FormParam`) with Spring equivalents (`@RequestMapping`, `@GetMapping`, `@PostMapping`, `@DeleteMapping`, `@PathVariable`, `@RequestParam`)\n\n2. **CDI -> Spring DI**: Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Inject` with `@RestController` + `@PersistenceContext`\n\n3. **JPA Metamodel -> String Attributes**: Replaced compile-time generated metamodel references (`Player_`, `Team_`, `League_`) with string-based criteria attributes (`\"position\"`, `\"salary\"`, etc.) since hibernate-jpamodelgen is not needed\n\n4. **Exception Handling**: Replaced `WebApplicationException` (JAX-RS) with `ResponseStatusException` (Spring)\n\n5. **Transaction Management**: Replaced `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n\n6. **Health**: Replaced SmallRye Health (`/q/health`) with Spring Boot Actuator (`/actuator/health`)\n\n### Error Handling\n\nNo unresolved errors. One issue was encountered and resolved during testing:\n- **URL encoding in smoke tests**: Paths with spaces (e.g., \"power forward\", \"Ian Carlyle\") needed proper URL encoding in the Python test client. Fixed by adding `urllib.parse.quote()` to the request helper."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":492,"cache_read_input_tokens":120227,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":492,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":809},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"28b9fbcd-f273-4b6e-b315-c50121e535b0","uuid":"dd159f30-2776-42fc-80a8-4205979ffb66"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":770726,"duration_api_ms":722263,"num_turns":66,"result":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Quarkus 3.30.5 -> Spring Boot 3.4.3\n**Overall outcome:** Success - all 137 smoke tests passing\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus BOM/dependencies with Spring Boot starter-parent and starters\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Migrated from Quarkus to Spring Boot property format\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/request/RequestBean.java: Refactored from JAX-RS to Spring MVC (@RestController, @GetMapping, etc.)\n- Dockerfile: Changed CMD from \"mvn quarkus:run\" to \"java -jar\" with Spring Boot fat JAR\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/RosterApplication.java: Spring Boot application entry point\n- smoke.py: Comprehensive smoke test suite (137 assertions)\n- CHANGELOG.md: Complete migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/client/RosterClient.java: JAX-RS client (incompatible without JAX-RS client dependency)\n- src/main/docker/Dockerfile.jvm: Quarkus-specific Dockerfile\n- src/main/docker/Dockerfile.legacy-jar: Quarkus-specific Dockerfile\n- src/main/docker/Dockerfile.native: Quarkus-specific Dockerfile\n- src/main/docker/Dockerfile.native-micro: Quarkus-specific Dockerfile\n\nUnchanged (compatible with both frameworks):\n- All entity classes (Player, Team, League, SummerLeague, WinterLeague) - standard Jakarta Persistence\n- All DTO classes (PlayerDetails, TeamDetails, LeagueDetails)\n- IncorrectSportException\n- Request interface\n```\n\n### Key Migration Decisions\n\n1. **JAX-RS -> Spring MVC**: Replaced all JAX-RS annotations (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`, `@DELETE`, `@PathParam`, `@QueryParam`, `@FormParam`) with Spring equivalents (`@RequestMapping`, `@GetMapping`, `@PostMapping`, `@DeleteMapping`, `@PathVariable`, `@RequestParam`)\n\n2. **CDI -> Spring DI**: Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Inject` with `@RestController` + `@PersistenceContext`\n\n3. **JPA Metamodel -> String Attributes**: Replaced compile-time generated metamodel references (`Player_`, `Team_`, `League_`) with string-based criteria attributes (`\"position\"`, `\"salary\"`, etc.) since hibernate-jpamodelgen is not needed\n\n4. **Exception Handling**: Replaced `WebApplicationException` (JAX-RS) with `ResponseStatusException` (Spring)\n\n5. **Transaction Management**: Replaced `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n\n6. **Health**: Replaced SmallRye Health (`/q/health`) with Spring Boot Actuator (`/actuator/health`)\n\n### Error Handling\n\nNo unresolved errors. One issue was encountered and resolved during testing:\n- **URL encoding in smoke tests**: Paths with spaces (e.g., \"power forward\", \"Ian Carlyle\") needed proper URL encoding in the Python test client. Fixed by adding `urllib.parse.quote()` to the request helper.","session_id":"28b9fbcd-f273-4b6e-b315-c50121e535b0","total_cost_usd":10.8511719,"usage":{"input_tokens":2354,"cache_creation_input_tokens":108276,"cache_read_input_tokens":4131093,"output_tokens":32408,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":108276}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":76873,"outputTokens":5018,"cacheReadInputTokens":478850,"cacheCreationInputTokens":35179,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.1550574000000001,"contextWindow":200000},"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":515,"outputTokens":123,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.0033900000000000002,"contextWindow":200000},"aws/claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":2354,"outputTokens":32408,"cacheReadInputTokens":4131093,"cacheCreationInputTokens":108276,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":10.6927245,"contextWindow":200000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"6c